Let me hep.

288
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:13,000
Slowly.

289
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,000
Wait.

290
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,000
Thanks a lot.

291
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:24,000
Yes.

292
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,000
Let her drink this.

293
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,000
Yes, Madam.

294
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,000
I'm not drinking this.

295
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,000
I don't know if it's poison.

296
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,000
Then throw it away.

297
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:44,000
Calm down, Madam. Madam Chan.

298
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,000
How can I calm down?

299
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,000
You also saw

300
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,000
that Madam has poison.

301
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,000
All that happened

302
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:54,000
is because Madam Li used poison to kill people.

303
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:56,000
The whole thing happened because of me?

304
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:58,000
And who told everything to Mr. Ma?

305
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:01,000
Letting enemies into our house, seeking for chance to attack our family.

306
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:03,000
But I've never killed anyone.

307
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:09,000
I just want my Yang to become the head of the Five Dragons Association.

308
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:11,000
I did it to protect my son as well.

309
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:13,000
You can't just blame me.

310
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:14,000
Don't say this.

311
00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:15,000
Please top.

312
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,000
Madam Li, Madam Chan.

313
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,000
You two claim to do it for your children.

314
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,000
But have you ever asked them if they want it?

315
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:26,000
If their mothers had to hurt others for themselves like this?

316
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:34,000
The Five Dragons Association has now collapsed.

317
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:37,000
I think we shouldn't have an argument.

318
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:42,000
We should discuss with each other.

319
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:43,000
What should we do?

320
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,000
How can we help Mr. Song and Mr. Tian?

321
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,000
The association no longer exists.

322
00:24:55,000 --> 00:25:00,000
The fortune, ranking, and power that I used to fight for.

323
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,000
It means nothing now.

324
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,000
But at least.

325
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,000
Yang is still here with you.

326
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:15,000
But my son Tian,

327
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,000
I don't know if he's still alive.

328
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:47,000
Jiu.

329
00:25:47,300 --> 00:25:48,000
Mei, Fu.

330
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,000
How did you get here?

331
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:04,000
Pin and Yang brought us here.

332
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:28,000
Her congenital disease makes her weak.

333
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,000
She was also poisoned by opium for a long time

334
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:34,000
until her body can't handle it.

335
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:37,000
So that means my sister…

336
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,000
We can still give her treatment.

337
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,000
Doctor Qi will treat you.

338
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,000
You'll be better now.

339
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:54,000
But we can't leave her like this long.

340
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:58,000
It's really hard to find the herbs used for the treatment.

341
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:02,000
But I know someone who can find it.

342
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:06,000
I need to travel to get the herbs by myself right now.

343
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,000
Thank you so much, Doctor.

344
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:22,000
Pin overheard the market vendors saying that

345
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:24,000
only a few workers managed to escape.

346
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:28,000
The rest are locked up in the house with Father, Tian and Bao.

347
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,000
But no one dared to inform the authorities

348
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:35,000
because the Japanese soldiers get involved in this.

349
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:39,000
Oh, how is Mr. Song doing now?

350
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,000
But Mr. Ma was poisoned by the beetle orchid.

351
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:45,000
He must be waiting for the antidote from me.

352
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,000
He wouldn't dare hurting them.

353
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:50,000
And do you really have an antidote?

354
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,000
No.

355
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:58,000
At that time, Jia lied to make Mr. Ma

356
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,000
release Tian and Mr. Song.

357
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,000
Then we can't use the same trick again.

358
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,000
Because if he finds out,

359
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:08,000
he will kill us for sure.

360
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:16,000
Don't worry about the antidote.

361
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,000
I'm preparing it.

362
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:29,000
Is this the resurrection powder that can be used as an antidote against the beetle orchid?

363
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,000
Right.

364
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:38,000
The beetle orchid is a poisonous mushroom produced in the human body.

365
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:43,000
It slowly sucks the blood of those poisoned to death.

366
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,000
To detoxify it,

367
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:50,000
we must use the herb that heats the blood

368
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:53,000
until the orchid dust can't grow

369
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:56,000
and finally dies.

370
00:28:57,000 --> 00:29:00,000
We need nine special herbs

371
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,000
with fire element.

372
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,000
Simmer it until thickened.

373
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:09,000
Wait for it to precipitate

374
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:13,000
and become crystallized and turn into powder.

375
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,000
But the longer we wait,

376
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,000
the more Mr. Ma will suffer.

377
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,000
And he might hurt Mr. Song and everyone.

378
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:29,000
How long will it take to finish, Doctor?

379
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,000
Three more days.

380
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:36,000
But I can't stay and watch until it is finished.

381
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:40,000
Because I need to retrieve the herbs to make medicine for Jiu's sister.

382
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,000
Madam Li,

383
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,000
Madam Chan,

384
00:29:44,300 --> 00:29:45,000
Bua,

385
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:48,000
help get Mr. Song out.

386
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,000
Congratulations, Ma.

387
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:17,000
Finally, you become the leader of the Five Dragons Association as you wish.

388
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,000
You got such a sweet mouth.

389
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:25,000
Are you afraid of dying like Chun?

390
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,000
Oh, brother.

391
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,000
You have proven yourself

392
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:32,000
that you are eligible to be a leader.

393
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,000
Why would I stop you?

394
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:38,000
Besides, I am a woman.

395
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,000
How can I fight against you?

396
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:45,000
Listen carefully.

397
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,000
I can control even Big Brother.

398
00:30:49,000 --> 00:30:53,000
So don't act like a snake that secretly bites me.

399
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:56,000
Or I won't let you live.

400
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:04,000
All the businesses of Song and Chun families,

401
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:06,000
I'll take care of everything myself,

402
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:08,000
including your teahouse too.

403
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,000
Big Brother is weird.

404
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:16,000
Letting a woman like you take care of the business for a long time.

405
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,000
From now on,

406
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,000
you just sit and relax.

407
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,000
Wait for the order from me.

408
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,000
Thank you Ma

409
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:31,000
for sharing my burden.

410
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,000
Sir.

411
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:43,000
Someone attaches this note on the front door.

412
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,000
Three more days,

413
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,000
I will bring you the antidote

414
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:54,000
in exchange for Mr. Song, Tian and Bao.

415
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,000
Don't harm everyone.

416
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,000
Three more days,

417
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:03,000
Li will exchange the antidote for the hostages.

418
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,000
You gather all our force,

419
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,000
including the soldiers lent by Captain Hiroshi.

420
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,000
I will surround and ambush Li.

421
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:13,000
Yes, Sir.

422
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:17,000
Prepare oil and gunpowder.

423
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:20,000
I will burn this place down.

424
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:25,000
You wait and see the end of those who dared to be enemies against me.

425
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:38,000
Come here quickly. Hurry up.

426
00:32:58,300 --> 00:33:02,300
Next time, you have to be careful when you walk and run.

427
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:06,300
So that you don't hurt yourself like this again.

428
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:15,300
If it hurts, just cry.

429
00:33:15,300 --> 00:33:18,300
I don't dare to cry. I'm afraid you will scold me.

430
00:33:18,300 --> 00:33:22,300
If you dare to say this out, then you're not really afraid of me.

431
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:25,300
Madam Li won't scold you.

432
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:28,300
She is Tian's mother. She must be kind like him.

433
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:33,300
Do you know Tian too?

434
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:38,300
When he was with you, how was he like?

435
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:42,300
Tian is kind. He likes to tell stories to me.

436
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:45,300
Take me to buy delicious snacks.

437
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:49,300
When I was sick, he also feed me medicine.

438
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:52,300
Yes, Tian once told us that

439
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:54,800
if Mei was happy, then Fu would be happy,

440
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:58,300
and Jiu and Tian would be happy as well.

441
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:05,300
You are afraid of losing power

442
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:09,300
and lose your leadership because of a son like me.

443
00:34:13,300 --> 00:34:14,300
Mother.

444
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:20,300
I just want to live happily.

445
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:26,300
You'll never be happy

446
00:34:28,300 --> 00:34:31,300
as long as you are like this.

447
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:36,300
When he was with me,

448
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:41,300
there are only sorrow,

449
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:44,300
fear and paranoia for him.

450
00:34:48,300 --> 00:34:49,300
Perhaps

451
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:55,300
it might be me that made him unhappy.

452
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,000
Father.

453
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:49,000
Are you feeling better?

454
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,000
It's all gone.

455
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:59,000
Five Dragons Association.

456
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:05,000
It is ruined.

457
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,000
I'm sorry.

458
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,000
I'm sorry, Father.

459
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:31,600
These are blankets for everyone.

460
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,600
And this is food.

461
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:37,600
I brought a lot. I'm afraid everyone will be hungry.

462
00:37:37,600 --> 00:37:39,600
Thanks.

463
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:42,000
The antidote will be completed soon.

464
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:45,600
We will take this medicine to help Father and Tian.

465
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,600
This job is very dangerous.

466
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:49,600
If anything happens to me,

467
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:50,600
You...

468
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:52,600
I'll find new boyfriend for sure.

469
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,600
What?

470
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:57,600
So you can't die.

471
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:02,600
Help Mr. Song and Tian and come back to me.

472
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:05,600
I have talked to my father already.

473
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:08,600
Although we don't have a lot of money now,

474
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:11,600
but we know someone who can help you escape from Mr. Ma.

475
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:21,600
Thank you for being by my side.

476
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:24,600
When I was in trouble,

477
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:28,600
you also stay here by my side.

478
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:32,600
If we don't help each other during a hard time, when will we do it?

479
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:37,600
But my family almost has nothing left.

480
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:40,600
If I come back alive,

481
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:45,600
are you really going to marry a poor guy like me?

482
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:47,600
My family is poor as well.

483
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:51,600
The first time we met, I still had to sell fake vase.

484
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:55,600
So I think the two of us are well suited to each other.

485
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:58,600
Just live a poor life together.

486
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:37,600
What?

487
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:40,600
You let me hide at Lady Pin's palace?

488
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:43,600
Yes, you're not feeling well yet.

489
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:46,900
I'll bring the antidote to exchange for the hostages myself.

490
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:47,900
No, I'll go with you too.

491
00:39:47,900 --> 00:39:48,600
Mom.

492
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,200
Why are you going?

493
00:39:50,200 --> 00:39:51,600
You'll be a burden to others.

494
00:39:52,600 --> 00:39:55,600
I won't let you save Mr. Song and take credit alone.

495
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:57,600
Madam, please be rational.

496
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:01,600
Do you want to know my reason?

497
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:02,600
Fine.

498
00:40:04,600 --> 00:40:05,600
Among us,

499
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:09,600
I am the closest with Mr. Ma.

500
00:40:11,600 --> 00:40:13,600
I know how to persuade him.

501
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:15,600
If I go,

502
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:19,600
there'll be more chance to help Mr. Song and Tian.

503
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:21,600
Are you going to help Tian?

504
00:40:33,600 --> 00:40:34,600
Right.

505
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:39,600
Well, Madam Li saved you and me once.

506
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:42,100
I don't want to be indebted.

507
00:40:42,100 --> 00:40:44,600
So we won't have to meet again in the next life.

508
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:49,600
Besides,

509
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:54,600
the Five Dragons Association no longer existed.

510
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:57,600
I have no reason to let Tian die.

511
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,600
If you're going,

512
00:41:07,600 --> 00:41:09,600
don't be a burden to others.

513
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:14,600
The medicine will finish soon.

514
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:17,600
We can help Tian and Mr. Song.

515
00:41:57,600 --> 00:41:59,600
I'll be right back, Captain.

516
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:12,300
I have investigated, Madam.

517
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:15,600
The Japanese don't fully support Mr. Ma.

518
00:42:15,600 --> 00:42:17,600
They just wanted to use him.

519
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:19,600
If they are in trouble,

520
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:21,600
they'll definitely kick Mr. Ma out.

521
00:42:21,600 --> 00:42:22,600
Are you sure?

522
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:24,600
Yes, Madam.

523
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:29,100
The captain also told me that the Japanese soldiers are at odds with each other.

524
00:42:29,100 --> 00:42:31,900
If the other party caught that the captain is messing with Thais,

525
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:33,600
they won't let him go.

526
00:43:03,600 --> 00:43:04,600
Press it.

527
00:43:14,600 --> 00:43:16,600
Tian's handkerchief.

528
00:43:27,600 --> 00:43:29,600
Jiu, take it easy.

529
00:43:30,600 --> 00:43:33,600
I'm confident that we will be able to help Mr. Song and Tian out.

530
00:43:34,600 --> 00:43:36,600
You'll surely meet Tian again.

531
00:43:42,600 --> 00:43:44,600
You don't see that the love between me and Tian…

532
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:47,600
is disgusting?

533
00:43:49,600 --> 00:43:51,600
It's not my duty to judge

534
00:43:52,600 --> 00:43:55,600
what kind of love is disgusting, or not disgusting.

535
00:43:57,600 --> 00:43:58,600
You too.

536
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:00,600
Don't let anyone judge you.

537
00:44:02,600 --> 00:44:06,600
Don't tie your own happiness to other people's thoughts.

538
00:44:12,600 --> 00:44:13,600
You know what?

539
00:44:14,600 --> 00:44:16,600
I have raised Tian since he was little.

540
00:44:17,600 --> 00:44:19,600
He is kind,

541
00:44:20,600 --> 00:44:21,600
and humble.

542
00:44:23,600 --> 00:44:28,600
He always cares about the feelings of those around him to make them happy.

543
00:44:29,300 --> 00:44:32,600
No matter how miserable he was, he never complained.

544
00:44:33,600 --> 00:44:35,600
I'm glad that

545
00:44:36,600 --> 00:44:37,600
now,

546
00:44:38,600 --> 00:44:40,600
you've become his happiness.

547
00:45:01,600 --> 00:45:02,600
Madam.

548
00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:24,600
Herbal tonic

549
00:45:25,600 --> 00:45:29,600
to restore your strength to fight with Mr. Ma's gang.

550
00:45:31,600 --> 00:45:33,600
Thank you, Madam.

551
00:45:48,600 --> 00:45:49,600
Jiu.

552
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:53,600
Drink it.

553
00:45:54,600 --> 00:45:57,600
Madam Li has carefully boiled it for you.

554
00:46:52,600 --> 00:46:53,600
Tian.

555
00:46:58,600 --> 00:46:59,600
Tian.

556
00:47:01,600 --> 00:47:02,600
Tian.

557
00:47:03,600 --> 00:47:04,600
Jiu.

558
00:47:06,600 --> 00:47:07,600
How did get here?

559
00:47:08,600 --> 00:47:11,600
Tian, I'm coming to check the area so I can find a way to help you.

560
00:47:12,600 --> 00:47:14,600
Doctor Qi is cooking the antidote now.

561
00:47:15,100 --> 00:47:16,600
We'll take that medicine to save you and Mr. Song.

562
00:47:18,600 --> 00:47:20,600
How are Mother and everyone?

563
00:47:21,600 --> 00:47:22,600
Everyone is safe.

564
00:47:24,600 --> 00:47:25,600
Except...

565
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:28,600
Jia.

566
00:47:31,600 --> 00:47:32,600
Jia?

567
00:47:42,600 --> 00:47:43,600
And how are you, Tian?

568
00:47:48,600 --> 00:47:50,600
Did they hurt you this much?

569
00:47:51,600 --> 00:47:52,600
Hang in there.

570
00:47:53,600 --> 00:47:54,600
I'll come back to help you.

571
00:47:55,600 --> 00:47:57,600
We'll leave all the chaos behind

572
00:47:58,600 --> 00:48:00,600
and live the life I promised you.

573
00:48:01,100 --> 00:48:02,600
I'm fine, Jiu,

574
00:48:03,600 --> 00:48:05,600
but you have to help my father.

575
00:48:06,600 --> 00:48:07,600
He's seriously ill.

576
00:48:08,600 --> 00:48:09,600
He's suffering

577
00:48:10,600 --> 00:48:12,600
because he's disappointed in me.

578
00:48:14,600 --> 00:48:16,600
I don't want anything to happen to him.

579
00:48:17,600 --> 00:48:18,600
please help my father.

580
00:48:19,600 --> 00:48:20,600
Please.

581
00:48:21,600 --> 00:48:22,600
Don't worry.

582
00:48:23,600 --> 00:48:25,600
You and your father must be safe.

583
00:48:27,600 --> 00:48:28,600
I promise with my life.

584
00:49:14,600 --> 00:49:15,600
Jiu.

585
00:49:15,900 --> 00:49:18,600
Get out now. They'll see you.

586
00:49:20,600 --> 00:49:21,600
Be careful.

587
00:49:22,000 --> 00:49:22,600
I'll be right back to save you.

588
00:50:17,600 --> 00:50:19,600
How was it? Have you met Father and Tian?

589
00:50:23,600 --> 00:50:24,600
How are they?

590
00:50:25,600 --> 00:50:26,600
Are Tian and Father injured?

591
00:50:27,600 --> 00:50:28,600
Both of them are safe.

592
00:50:35,600 --> 00:50:36,600
Jia.

593
00:50:37,600 --> 00:50:40,600
Tomorrow, I'm going to help Mr. Song and Tian.

594
00:50:42,600 --> 00:50:44,600
May your soul

595
00:50:45,600 --> 00:50:47,600
bless us to succeed.

596
00:50:49,600 --> 00:50:50,600
If I survive,

597
00:50:52,600 --> 00:50:54,600
I'll come back to arrange a grand funeral for you.

598
00:51:04,600 --> 00:51:07,600
Chan and I will negotiate with Mr. Ma,

599
00:51:08,100 --> 00:51:08,600
which he probably won't give up easily.

600
00:51:09,600 --> 00:51:11,600
But I will try to buy the time as long as possible.

601
00:51:12,600 --> 00:51:17,600
Jiu said that Mr. Song and Tian are locked up in the wood shed at the back of the house.

602
00:51:18,600 --> 00:51:21,600
There's a small exit blocked by the trees in that area.

603
00:51:22,300 --> 00:51:23,600
Mr. Ma probably didn't know about it.

604
00:51:24,600 --> 00:51:28,600
You and Jiu go in to help Mr. Song and Tian out and go through that way.

605
00:51:29,200 --> 00:51:29,700
As for Pin,

606
00:51:30,600 --> 00:51:31,600
and Bua,

607
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:32,600
wait outside.

608
00:51:33,600 --> 00:51:34,600
When the two are rescued,

609
00:51:35,600 --> 00:51:38,600
everyone gets in Pin's car and flee as quickly as possible.

610
00:51:39,600 --> 00:51:40,600
And what about you and Madam Li?

611
00:51:42,600 --> 00:51:43,600
I still have beetle orchid left.

612
00:51:44,600 --> 00:51:46,600
I'll use it to deal with Mr. Ma and quickly escape.

613
00:51:47,600 --> 00:51:48,600
Madam.

614
00:51:49,600 --> 00:51:51,600
What if it doesn't succeed?

615
00:51:54,600 --> 00:51:56,600
Just talk about later.

616
00:51:57,600 --> 00:51:58,600
It's settled then.

617
00:51:59,600 --> 00:52:04,600
I'm afraid that Ma is also preparing a plan to welcome you, Madam.

618
00:52:18,600 --> 00:52:19,600
How did you get here?

619
00:52:20,600 --> 00:52:21,600
And how do you know that we are here?

620
00:52:22,600 --> 00:52:25,600
Didn't Jiu spy at Song family's house this morning?

621
00:52:28,600 --> 00:52:29,600
Mud is my staff.

622
00:52:30,600 --> 00:52:32,600
But it will be too long to tell the story now.

623
00:52:33,600 --> 00:52:35,600
Let's get to the point.

624
00:52:36,600 --> 00:52:39,600
You can't go back to your home now.

625
00:52:40,600 --> 00:52:41,600
Why do we have to believe you?

626
00:52:42,600 --> 00:52:43,600
From the beginning,

627
00:52:44,100 --> 00:52:46,600
you must have sent Mud to investigate the news, right?

628
00:52:47,100 --> 00:52:48,600
How much did you sell the news from Song family?

629
00:52:49,600 --> 00:52:51,600
The leaked information from the house,

630
00:52:52,600 --> 00:52:55,600
I think it came from you, Chan.

631
00:52:56,600 --> 00:52:57,600
I come here today

632
00:52:58,600 --> 00:53:00,600
because I know that Ma prepares to kill everyone

633
00:53:01,600 --> 00:53:04,600
and burn down Song family's house.

634
00:53:05,600 --> 00:53:07,600
How can we believe you?

635
00:53:08,600 --> 00:53:10,600
How will all of us know that you isn't working with Mr. Ma?

636
00:53:10,900 --> 00:53:11,600
If I cooperates with him,

637
00:53:12,600 --> 00:53:15,600
isn't it easier to let them kill you here?

638
00:53:19,600 --> 00:53:22,600
I know that you guys don't trust me

639
00:53:24,600 --> 00:53:26,600
and thought that I was a hypocrite.

640
00:53:32,600 --> 00:53:33,600
But you know it well, don't you, Li?

641
00:53:35,600 --> 00:53:36,600
In this world,

642
00:53:37,600 --> 00:53:39,600
it's always cruel to women like us.

643
00:53:41,600 --> 00:53:44,600
Especially for the widow whose husband died like me.

644
00:53:46,600 --> 00:53:48,600
Staying in the Five Dragons Association

645
00:53:49,600 --> 00:53:50,600
is not easy.

646
00:53:52,600 --> 00:53:54,600
I am underestimated

647
00:53:55,600 --> 00:53:57,600
and also the target to be taken advantage of.

648
00:53:58,600 --> 00:53:59,600
Because I'm a single woman,

649
00:54:00,600 --> 00:54:04,600
I have to struggle in every way possible to maintain my business.

650
00:54:08,600 --> 00:54:10,600
Aren't you afraid

651
00:54:11,600 --> 00:54:14,600
that Mr. Ma will find out that you sided with us?

652
00:54:16,600 --> 00:54:17,600
Of course.

653
00:54:18,600 --> 00:54:19,600
But I have to do.

654
00:54:20,600 --> 00:54:25,600
Allowing evil guy that killed his own brother like Ma to come to power

655
00:54:26,600 --> 00:54:28,600
will make all of us suffer in the future.

656
00:54:31,600 --> 00:54:33,600
I may not be a good woman,

657
00:54:34,600 --> 00:54:38,600
But I am not bad enough to support an evil man like Ma.

658
00:54:40,600 --> 00:54:42,600
If you don’t want us to go help Mr. Song,

659
00:54:42,900 --> 00:54:43,600
what should we do?

660
00:54:46,600 --> 00:54:47,600
About that,

661
00:54:48,600 --> 00:54:50,600
leave it to me.

662
00:55:09,600 --> 00:55:11,600
Father, Father.

663
00:55:12,600 --> 00:55:13,600
Father.

664
00:55:14,000 --> 00:55:14,600
Father.

665
00:55:21,600 --> 00:55:22,600
Big brother.

666
00:55:24,600 --> 00:55:25,600
Big brother.

667
00:55:27,900 --> 00:55:28,600
Big brother.

668
00:55:31,900 --> 00:55:32,600
Big brother.

669
00:55:36,600 --> 00:55:37,600
Big brother.

670
00:55:37,900 --> 00:55:38,600
Zhang.

671
00:55:46,600 --> 00:55:48,600
Big Brother, please sit down.

672
00:55:58,600 --> 00:56:00,600
Am I really dead?

673
00:56:05,600 --> 00:56:07,600
Drink it first.

674
00:56:11,600 --> 00:56:13,600
This must be Meng Po soup

675
00:56:14,600 --> 00:56:17,600
given to the ghost to wipe the memories, right?

676
00:56:20,600 --> 00:56:22,600
What are you talking about?

677
00:56:23,600 --> 00:56:26,600
This is the Keemun tea that you like.

678
00:56:37,600 --> 00:56:38,600
Zhang.

679
00:56:41,600 --> 00:56:42,600
Since you were gone,

680
00:56:46,600 --> 00:56:48,600
everything was never the same.

681
00:56:49,600 --> 00:56:51,600
The Five Dragons Association had collapsed.

682
00:56:55,600 --> 00:56:56,600
Tian is also...

683
00:57:00,600 --> 00:57:02,600
Probably because of your curse.

684
00:57:03,100 --> 00:57:03,600
Oh my god.

685
00:57:04,600 --> 00:57:05,600
Are you saying that

686
00:57:07,600 --> 00:57:09,600
what I said before I died

687
00:57:10,600 --> 00:57:11,600
caused something like this to happen?

688
00:57:13,600 --> 00:57:16,600
I never thought that you would kill yourself.

689
00:57:17,600 --> 00:57:19,600
I did it to protect the association.

690
00:57:21,600 --> 00:57:23,600
I have never hated you.

691
00:57:26,600 --> 00:57:28,600
But I don't understand people like you.

692
00:57:31,600 --> 00:57:33,600
In this world, no one can understand everyone.

693
00:57:35,600 --> 00:57:36,600
Even ourselves,

694
00:57:37,600 --> 00:57:40,600
sometimes we don't even understand ourselves, do we?

695
00:57:42,600 --> 00:57:45,600
And I didn't want anyone to understand me.

696
00:57:49,600 --> 00:57:51,600
I don't even want anyone to pity me

697
00:57:52,600 --> 00:57:55,600
because we only pity those who are struggling

698
00:57:56,600 --> 00:57:57,600
or inferior to us only.

699
00:58:00,600 --> 00:58:02,600
I don't think that

700
00:58:03,600 --> 00:58:05,600
I am inferior to anyone.

701
00:58:09,600 --> 00:58:10,600
So what do you want?

702
00:58:11,600 --> 00:58:13,600
Respect.

703
00:58:15,600 --> 00:58:17,600
Respect me as a human being.

704
00:58:19,600 --> 00:58:20,600
Not higher

705
00:58:22,600 --> 00:58:23,600
nor lower than others.

706
00:58:27,600 --> 00:58:30,600
Just like other people, like an equal.

707
00:58:35,600 --> 00:58:37,600
Tian also said this.

708
00:58:41,600 --> 00:58:42,600
As a human being.

709
00:58:44,600 --> 00:58:45,600
That's all.

710
00:58:46,600 --> 00:58:50,600
Just this little thing that my son wants,

711
00:58:54,600 --> 00:58:55,600
but I still can't give him.

712
00:58:58,600 --> 00:58:59,600
It's a pity that I didn't understand this

713
00:59:03,600 --> 00:59:04,600
when I was still alive.

714
00:59:06,600 --> 00:59:07,600
You likes to talk nonsense.

715
00:59:08,600 --> 00:59:09,600
Why do you keep talking about death?

716
00:59:12,600 --> 00:59:14,600
If you don't want to watch opera with me,

717
00:59:17,600 --> 00:59:18,600
just go back.

718
00:59:22,600 --> 00:59:23,600
Father, Father.

719
00:59:23,900 --> 00:59:24,600
Father.

720
00:59:31,600 --> 00:59:32,600
Father.

721
00:59:32,900 --> 00:59:33,600
Tian.

722
00:59:43,600 --> 00:59:44,600
Father.

723
00:59:52,600 --> 00:59:54,600
Father, please drink some water.

724
01:00:32,600 --> 01:00:33,600
Do you feel better?

725
01:00:44,600 --> 01:00:45,600
I'm sorry.

726
01:00:48,600 --> 01:00:49,600
Why do you apologize to me?

727
01:00:53,600 --> 01:00:55,600
It's all because of me.

728
01:00:56,600 --> 01:00:58,600
Not at all.

729
01:01:00,600 --> 01:01:02,600
I am the cause of everything.

730
01:01:05,600 --> 01:01:06,600
If I wasn't like this,

731
01:01:07,600 --> 01:01:09,600
it wouldn't be a mess.

732
01:01:11,600 --> 01:01:14,600
And everyone doesn't have to suffer like this.

733
01:01:20,600 --> 01:01:21,600
No.

734
01:01:26,600 --> 01:01:28,600
Because I am narrow-minded.

735
01:01:31,600 --> 01:01:33,600
I forced Zhang to commit suicide.

736
01:01:36,600 --> 01:01:39,600
Your mother saw the fate of Zhang,

737
01:01:40,600 --> 01:01:43,600
so she didn't want you to end like that.

738
01:01:45,600 --> 01:01:47,600
Don't be angry with her.

739
01:01:48,600 --> 01:01:49,600
Not at all.

740
01:01:50,600 --> 01:01:52,600
I have never hold a grudge against Mother.

741
01:01:53,600 --> 01:01:54,600
I understand.

742
01:01:56,600 --> 01:01:57,600
She did it to protect me.

743
01:02:02,600 --> 01:02:03,600
If I…

744
01:02:05,600 --> 01:02:09,600
could be the son that you and Mother hoped for,

745
01:02:13,600 --> 01:02:15,600
everything wouldn't be like this, right?

746
01:02:18,600 --> 01:02:20,600
Parents gave birth to children,

747
01:02:21,600 --> 01:02:23,600
but not the owner of their lives.

748
01:02:27,600 --> 01:02:30,600
You have to carry too much of my hope.

749
01:02:36,600 --> 01:02:37,600
In the past,

750
01:02:38,600 --> 01:02:39,600
I had made you

751
01:02:41,600 --> 01:02:43,600
feel that being yourself is wrong,

752
01:02:44,600 --> 01:02:46,600
or inferior to others.

753
01:02:48,600 --> 01:02:49,600
I'm sorry.

754
01:02:56,600 --> 01:02:58,600
If we can survive,

755
01:03:02,600 --> 01:03:04,600
from now on,

756
01:03:08,600 --> 01:03:09,600
how you want to live,

757
01:03:12,600 --> 01:03:15,600
who you want to love,

758
01:03:17,600 --> 01:03:19,600
what kind of life you want,

759
01:03:23,600 --> 01:03:25,600
it's up to you, Tian.

760
01:03:28,600 --> 01:03:31,600
Choose the live you want to have,

761
01:03:35,600 --> 01:03:37,600
live a happy life.

762
01:03:40,600 --> 01:03:41,600
I will respect your decision.

763
01:03:45,600 --> 01:03:46,600
Father.

764
01:04:45,600 --> 01:04:46,600
Resurrection powder.

765
01:05:11,600 --> 01:05:12,600
Madam.

766
01:05:14,600 --> 01:05:15,600
Everyone is ready.

767
01:05:43,600 --> 01:05:45,600
How many days have we been locked up?

768
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:46,600
I can't stand it anymore.

769
01:05:48,600 --> 01:05:50,600
Everyone, hang in there.

770
01:05:50,900 --> 01:05:51,600
Be patient.

771
01:05:52,600 --> 01:05:55,600
If Madam Li give the antidote to Mr. Ma, everyone will survive.

772
01:05:56,600 --> 01:05:58,600
She won't leave us for sure.

773
01:06:05,600 --> 01:06:07,600
Hey what are you doing?

774
01:06:07,900 --> 01:06:08,600
What are you doing to us again?

775
01:06:09,600 --> 01:06:13,600
Mr. Ma ordered us to burn and blow up this place today.

776
01:06:14,600 --> 01:06:15,600
Wait.

777
01:06:16,600 --> 01:06:17,600
What do you mean?

778
01:06:18,600 --> 01:06:19,600
Didn't he say that he will let us go if he gets the medicine?

779
01:06:20,600 --> 01:06:22,600
Hey, put the buckets down

780
01:06:23,600 --> 01:06:26,600
and bury the dynamite around. Quickly.

781
01:06:27,600 --> 01:06:29,600
No, you can't. Don’t do it. Put it down.

782
01:06:34,600 --> 01:06:35,400
Hurry.

783
01:06:37,600 --> 01:06:39,600
Thermite.

784
01:06:45,600 --> 01:06:47,600
Be careful.

785
01:06:48,100 --> 01:06:50,600
Patrol around. Don't let any single person escape.

786
01:07:19,600 --> 01:07:21,600
You must open it.

787
01:07:25,600 --> 01:07:26,600
What's the matter?

788
01:07:37,600 --> 01:07:39,600
Great you're here.

789
01:07:40,600 --> 01:07:43,600
I've brought the gift to congratulate you

790
01:07:44,600 --> 01:07:47,600
and the girls to entertain you guys.

791
01:07:48,600 --> 01:07:50,600
But they wouldn't let me go in.

792
01:07:51,600 --> 01:07:53,600
They insisted to let me open the chest.

793
01:08:17,600 --> 01:08:19,600
My teahouse account

794
01:08:20,600 --> 01:08:22,600
and a list of clients.

795
01:08:24,600 --> 01:08:28,600
It contains information that I have obtained

796
01:08:29,600 --> 01:08:31,600
for use in business negotiations.

797
01:08:33,600 --> 01:08:35,600
I have been collecting it for a long time.

798
01:08:36,600 --> 01:08:37,600
But today,

799
01:08:38,600 --> 01:08:40,600
I think it's the time to give it to you.

800
01:08:41,600 --> 01:08:42,600
As for the liquor,

801
01:08:44,600 --> 01:08:46,600
I brought them to celebrate together.

802
01:09:16,600 --> 01:09:19,600
Ma, would you like some alcohol?

803
01:09:22,200 --> 01:09:25,600
It has been fermented for twenty years.

804
01:09:26,600 --> 01:09:27,600
It's the signature recipe from my teahouse.

805
01:10:38,600 --> 01:10:40,600
The Japanese soldiers are all at the party.

806
01:10:41,600 --> 01:10:42,600
There are only Mr. Ma's subordinates in the house.

807
01:10:43,600 --> 01:10:44,600
You can follow the plan, Madam.

808
01:11:05,600 --> 01:11:07,600
Yang, be careful.

809
01:11:19,600 --> 01:11:20,600
Be careful.

810
01:11:24,600 --> 01:11:25,600
Stop!

811
01:11:26,600 --> 01:11:27,600
Go!

812
01:11:27,900 --> 01:11:28,600
What should we do?
